third-party asset states a different license.

This repository is created as a personal learning workspace for becoming a
job-ready Java full-stack developer. It includes frontend fundamentals, Java,
Spring Boot, databases, APIs, authentication, security, testing, deployment,
system design, AI engineering, interview preparation, and portfolio projects.

